{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "us-som-org-intent-2026-11-full",
    "name": "Lenovo — SOM Organizational Intent Setup (US 3.2.2)",
    "description": "End-to-end Postman collection for **User Story 3.2.2 — Organizational Intent Setup** and **3.2.3 — Delete Intent Card**.\n\n**Prereqs**\n1. D365 Sales running: `uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000` (v0.22.0+)\n2. Postgres migrations:\n   - `sql/2026_10_som_interview_setup.sql`\n   - `sql/2026_11_som_organizational_intent.sql`\n3. Collection variables (optional): `adminUserId`, `d365BaseUrl`\n\n**Run order**\nExecute folders `00` → `09` top-to-bottom. Folder `04` saves all 6 cards; folder `09` deletes Outcome (run after `04`).\n\n**Intent types:** outcome · motion · focus · behavioral · constraint · tradeoff\n\n**Linked:** SPRINT_2_US322_SOM_ORGANIZATIONAL_INTENT_BACKEND_HANDOFF.md",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "d365BaseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminUserId", "value": "admin@lenovo.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "intentType", "value": "outcome", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "metricId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "focusExpiryDate", "value": "2026-09-30", "type": "string" }
  ],
